--[[
    Da7muLibrary  –  Polished Edition
    Original design by Da7mu

    v3 Changes:
      • Lucide icon support via Footagesus/Icons — pass "lucide:house" anywhere
        an icon is accepted (Page, Window hub icon, etc.)
      • Spring-physics drag delay — window smoothly follows the cursor with
        velocity, giving a premium inertial feel.
      • Notifications fade + scale in on appear, fade + scale out on dismiss.
      • Dropdowns fade + scale in when opened, fade + scale out when closed.
      • Nav tab icons are pinned flush-left inside the button, independent of
        the text label, so they can't overlap.
      • All prior bug-fixes retained (dropdown clipping, connection leaks, blur
        NaN guard, viewport clamping, separator return value).
]]

